31:33.133 --> 31:35.093
That's why I developed the process.

31:35.247 --> 31:38.874
I didn't want to watch my daughter go
through the pain that I endured only to have

31:38.930 --> 31:41.945
what other girls were lucky enough to be born with.

31:42.631 --> 31:45.417
So let's get you scheduled here.

31:45.473 --> 31:46.621
Yes please.

31:49.704 --> 31:51.861
