35:26.522 --> 35:27.698
You're funny.

35:27.726 --> 35:29.966
Yeah. And cute, huh?

35:32.585 --> 35:34.768
Okay, jason, look, I'm being serious.

35:34.992 --> 35:35.986
All right.

35:37.429 --> 35:39.865
Back in freshman year, I, uh,

35:39.893 --> 35:42.218
made the cheerleading squad.

35:43.058 --> 35:44.864
